// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P4150269992" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Steam Powered Pigeon</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a steam powered pigeon flapping its tin wings in the air before crashing to the ground. You look it over and listen as it begins to bark out instructions.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>HAIL LORD NEMESIS (of course, Nemesis),<br><br>THE FINAL STAGE HAS BEEN SET. THE ARTIFACT TO BREACH THE SHADOW SHARD HAS BEEN OBTAINED. THE BASE SHALL BE FORTIFIED WITH MORE SOLDIERS, WHILE THE HEROES WILL BE BUSY WITH YET MORE RULARUU. THE VILLAIN MANGLE HAS AGREED TO HELP IN FINISHING THE RITUAL. ALL HANDS ARE TO REPORT TO THE WAREHOUSE PRINTED ON THE SIDE OF THE BIRD TO ENSURE NO HEROES CAN DESTROY THE ARTIFACT.<br><br>SIGNED,<br><br>BIRD MESSENGER 7 </scale></font></color><br><br>Looks like the Nemesis army is planning on unleashing the menace of Rularuu on Paragon to cover their own actions within the Shadow Shard. You figure an artifact with <i>that</i> much power could sell for quite a bit on the black market, especially if it has to do with the Shadow Shard. The one downside is that there's a good chance there are more of these steam powered pidgeons out there, meaning someone else could stroll along and either stop this ritual or get the artifact before you can."
// Answer Text :
"P3454039595" "Hero: Stop the ritual and get the artifact to sell!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
"P1342464925" "Now is not a good time to investigate this tip.  Wait until you are within the streets of Paragon City before you attempt any investigation."
// Answer Text :
"P385518726" "Investigate this tip later"
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


