// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P1931455110" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Bootleg Video Case</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find what is clearly a bootleg copy of a movie released recently. The actors on the cover seem to be D-Listers that look somewhat similar to the main actors of the film. Just for fun, you open it up and see a complex-looking video device inside instead of a crummy looking CD. You push a button on the video and watch...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>You see an image of a woman being held hostage with two guards from Malta around her. One man points to the camera.<br><br>'This woman has been a thorn in Malta's side for too long. We know all about her involvement with Crimson and Indigo, and now she is going to <i>die</i>, unless the Paragon Police pay us a hefty sum of money for her release. The address to drop the money off is within this case. If you know what's good for you, you'll give us the money to save this woman's life.'<br><br></scale></font></color><br><br>You can only wonder how this woman knows Crimson and Indigo, but this whole setup gives you an idea of how you could profit off of the situation. You could go in there and take down Malta and take whatever ransom money is given to them for yourself! No harm, no foul. The woman will still get rescued, and you'll earn some money to use down the line."
// Answer Text :
"P2576088617" "HERO: Take Malta's ransom for yourself!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


