// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P4068665945" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hello? Bonjour? Ciao? HOLA?!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You overhear this phrase several times in the area, as if someone is trying to get your attention. You look around and spot a small microbead stuck on the side of your foot. You pick it up and answer back...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Hello! Hello, thank goodness someone answered! My name is Werner Meinz, and you are the last person that I will speak to in my life. I was a former member of the Council before joining a man named Hollow Point in his attempt to overthrow the government. This time, however, he has gone too far. He has recruited the villain Polar Shift and has created devices that will amplify her cold powers. He plans on freezing over Paragon City and using it as an example of his power to all of the world's governments! <br><br>I tried to stop them, but I could not. Please, whoever is listening, if you have an ounce of decency in you, please go to the laboratory at the following location. If nothing is done soon, everyone in Paragon will be frozen solid!<br><br></scale></font></color><br><br>You try to respond to the man, but all you hear are the sounds of gunfire, followed by silence. If what he's said is true, Paragon City is in danger of becoming a city of ice, with you inside of it! You're not too sure how long there is, but there's probably not enough time for the <i>proper</i> heroes of Paragon to come save the day..."
// Answer Text :
"P712852911" "HERO: Stop Hollow Point and Polar Shift's plans."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


