// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P3606433545" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Replica Rikti Sword</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a replica Rikti Sword made of plastic. Whoever made it managed to match the same glow that the swords are known to have. Around the hilt you find a wrapped piece of paper. You open it up and read it over...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>We've found the stash of Rikti supplies. They've got one of their bases deep beneath Paragon City, biding their time. If we hit it hard and fast, we can steal all the supplies and make a killing on the market! These things are going for a ridiculous amount; mainly since we bought the remaining supply and jacked up the prices. Anyway, here's the location. Whatever you do, <i>don't lose the sword</i>, we need it back to prove the deal was legit. Don't ask why, it's a weird buyer.</scale></font></color><br><br>Whoever this sword was meant for clearly isn't around to use it anymore. And now, you've got a location of a supply of Rikti weapons that you could use to make a good amount of money on the market. Why not take advantage of the situation to make an easy dollar?"
// Answer Text :
"P2279480313" "HERO: Sell off the Rikti weapons!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


