// Page RoguetoHero Text :
"P691939258" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Gold Plated Monocle</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a gold plated monocle just laying on the ground. You pick it up and see that it's actually just fake gold, so it wouldn't really sell for any money. However, there seems to be some sort of microchip embedded into the glass part of the monocle. You put in some legwork to get the microchip analyzed and find that there was a video contained inside of it...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>The video seems to be taken in an abandoned laboratory. You see Crey scientists doing experiments on one of the Cabal witches. A scientist clears his throat and begins to speak in a monotone voice, describing how they are trying to figure out a way to scientifically measure the magic that the Cabal uses in order to transplant it into the Crey Paragon Protectors. The witch lets out a scream, pleading for anyone to help her and that whoever helps will be greatly rewarded. At that point, one of the Crey guards knocks out the witch. As the video finishes, the Crey scientist reveals the location of the lab and that the video is for classified eyes only. </scale></font></color><br><br>Yet another unethical and ridiculous experiment being performed by those within Crey. What a <i>surprise</i>. What <i>really</i> caught your attention was the witch offering a possible reward for her rescue. This might be something that you could make a profit on, as long as it isn't too difficult going up against Crey."
// Answer Text :
"P1613801692" "HERO: Save the Cabal from Crey!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

